Overview

This project demonstrates how to analyze web server logs to detect common attack techniques including directory fuzzing, brute-force attacks, and SQL injection (SQLi).

Attack Summary
1. Directory Fuzzing (Reconnaissance)
Attacker Tool (User-Agent): FFUF v2.1.0
