The attacker used FFUF to scan the web application for hidden directories and files.

2. Brute Force Attack
Target Page: /login.php
<img width="1907" height="793" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a9192524-25f6-465c-a39f-0b2935886429" />


The attacker performed repeated login attempts using automated requests, indicating a brute-force attack.

3. SQL Injection Attack
Target Page: /changeusername.php
Payload Used:
' OR '1'='1
<img width="1918" height="835" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/dbc9ae23-e65d-4fbf-82b7-d3c590e002af" />


